Student Grade Calculator
📖 Overview

The Student Grade Calculator is a Java-based console application that calculates a student's total marks, average percentage, grade, and pass/fail status based on marks entered for multiple subjects. The application provides an easy and efficient way to evaluate academic performance.

This project demonstrates fundamental Java programming concepts such as user input handling, conditional statements, arithmetic operations, and decision-making.

✨ Features
📝 Accepts student name as input
📚 Takes marks for multiple subjects
➕ Calculates total marks obtained
📊 Calculates average percentage
🏅 Assigns grades automatically
✅ Displays Pass/Fail status
💻 User-friendly console interface
🛠️ Technologies Used
Java
Visual Studio Code (VS Code)
Git
GitHub
